# Release artifacts from build-all.sh
out/

# Regression test artifacts — only the canonical baseline PNGs should be tracked.
# *.diff.png   — pixel-difference image from `magick compare`
# *.actual.png — actual capture when it diverges from baseline
# *.png.new    — proposed new baseline (review, then rename to .png to commit)
**/baseline/*.diff.png
**/baseline/*.actual.png
**/baseline/*.png.new
